headline: Coastal Bend LNG selects ConocoPhillips’ Optimized Cascade® Process technology
summary: HOUSTON, August 04, 2025--Today, Coastal Bend LNG announced it has selected ConocoPhillips’ Optimized Cascade® Process liquefaction technology for its planned natural gas liquefaction and export facility on the Texas Gulf Coast. Coastal Bend LNG’s planned development includes multiple liquefaction trains, cogeneration, LNG storage tanks, and export facilities.
